CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 25, 2011

[Cite as 02/25/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-846.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1538. State ex rel. Waters v. WEK Acquisition Corp., Inc.

Franklin App. No. 09AP-337, 2010-Ohio-3520. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County.

Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
